c: 2
v: 71
t: "(Musa)) said, \"As a matter of fact, He says that this cow is not yoked or burdened. It does not plough the land, nor does it irrigate the field. It is unscathed, and without a blemish; it is free of faults.\" They said, \"Now you have brought the truth.\" Then they slaughtered it, but they almost didn´t do it"